DESCRIPTION: Shows how to set multiple context values in a single operation, available in Node-RED 0.19 or later.
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-red/node-red.github.io/blob/master/docs/user-guide/writing-functions.md#2025-04-09_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
