TITLE: Sending Multiple Messages to Multiple Outputs in Node-RED
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates sending multiple messages to different outputs. Three messages are sent to the first output in sequence, while one message is sent to the second output.
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-red/node-red.github.io/blob/master/docs/user-guide/writing-functions.md#2025-04-09_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
