TITLE: Splitting Text into Multiple Messages in Node-RED
DESCRIPTION: Splits the incoming payload text by spaces and returns a separate message for each word, demonstrating how to generate multiple messages from a single input.
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-red/node-red.github.io/blob/master/docs/user-guide/writing-functions.md#2025-04-09_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
