TITLE: Implementing Node Property Usage
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript implementation showing how to use node properties in the runtime
SOURCE: https://github.com/node-red/node-red.github.io/blob/master/docs/creating-nodes/properties.md#2025-04-09_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function LowerCaseNode(config) {
    RED.nodes.createNode(this,config);
    this.prefix = config.prefix;
    var node = this;
    this.on('input', function(msg) {
        msg.payload = node.prefix + msg.payload.toLowerCase();
        node.send(msg);
    });
}
```

